{"tid":1146813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【噤聲惡法】新加坡立法打擊假新聞 惡意散播者最高可囚10年","createTime":"2019-05-09T12:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T03:05:38.000Z","uid":158272,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1263f07a647dd03560ebab0560ded153929cd9eb","tid":1146813,"uid":158272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T12:55:47.000Z","msg":"新加坡周三通過打擊假新聞法例，容許法庭嚴懲發佈假新聞或資訊的個人及網絡平台，惡意散播者最高可囚10年。「人權觀察」批評新法例會產生寒蟬效應，對在網上發表意見的普通新加坡人是一場「災難」，同時打擊很多網上新聞平台的獨立性。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡國會周三以72票贊成、9票反對的大比數通過《防止網絡虛假資訊與操控法案》，在新法之下，涉嫌惡意散播假資訊、損害公共利益者，最多可被判監10年，罰款100萬新加坡元（約575萬港元）。"},{"pid":"ee810f05fafecc800e2f8d1cf0c3133160b3d597","tid":1146813,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae9e49a7a30d6f7f7306915e9b76152a307ba89","tid":1146813,"uid":52215,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"新加坡先恐怖，表面民主其實獨裁到癲"},{"pid":"eb7e13477911daed4c5fd3f02c6e7bcd90684b46","tid":1146813,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"隨時新聞封鎖, 河蟹傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4cd387b645835818db38210fda14a6ab31a99e","tid":1146813,"uid":71768,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T13:32:47.000Z","msg":"新加坡當人民係寵物狗 高級小小"},{"pid":"0043498667e2350d4e3e56fc825c7764c69873f0","tid":1146813,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:29:00.000Z","msg":"Content farms disaster"},{"pid":"b456a92e288786afb571119d8132a7b194f23284","tid":1146813,"uid":10692,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:32:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0d11e69d55d246c5f141a01038a5975a3b5e441","tid":1146813,"uid":10692,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除